mypy .
```

### Testing

```bash
# Run tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=.
```

## Docker

### Build locally

```bash
docker build -t ai-subtitle-translator .
```

### Multi-platform build

```bash
docker buildx build --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 -t ai-subtitle-translator .
```

